#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/jit.md:0
msgid "# triton.jit"
msgstr "# triton.jit"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/jit.md:2
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.jit(fn: T) -> JITFunction[T]\n"
"triton.jit(*, version=None, repr: Callable | None = None, launch_metadata: Callable | None = None, do_not_specialize: Iterable[int] | None = None, debug: bool | None = None, noinline: bool | None = None) -> Callable[[T], JITFunction[T]]\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/jit.md:4
msgid "使用 Triton 编译器的 JIT 编译函数的装饰器。"
msgstr "Decorator for JIT-compiled functions using the Triton compiler."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/jit.md:6
msgid "- 注：当调用 JIT 编译的函数时，如果参数具有 `.data_ptr()` 方法和 `.dtype` 属性，则会隐式转换为指针。"
msgstr "- Note: When calling a JIT-compiled function, if the argument has a `.data_ptr()` method and a `.dtype` attribute, it will be implicitly converted to a pointer."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/jit.md:8
msgid ""
"- 注：此函数将在 GPU 上编译和运行。它只能访问以下内容：\n"
"    - Python 原语，\n"
"    - Triton 包内的内置函数，\n"
"    - 此函数的参数，\n"
"    - 其他 JIT 编译的函数。\n"
msgstr ""
"- Note: This function will be compiled and executed on the GPU. It can only access the following:\n"
"    - Python primitives,\n"
"    - Built-in functions within the Triton package,\n"
"    - Parameters of this function,\n"
"    - Other JIT-compiled functions.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/triton/jit.md:10
msgid "**参数：**`fn (Callable)` - 要进行 JIT 编译的函数"
msgstr "**Parameters:** `fn (Callable)` - The function to be JIT compiled."

